---
import SectionHeader from '../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section id="reviews" class="bg-gv-black/30 py-24 3xl:py-48 4xl:py-64 px-6 relative">
    <div class="glow-blur absolute inset-0 bg-gv-blue opacity-5 animate-pulse-slow"></div>
    <div class="max-w-[1800px] 4xl:max-w-[2400px] mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="mb-12 3xl:mb-24 4xl:mb-32">
            <SectionHeader title="Trusted by the" accentText="City" accentColor="text-gv-green" alignment="center" />
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 3xl:gap-12 4xl:gap-16">
            <figure class="glass-morphism p-6 3xl:p-12 4xl:p-16 rounded-2xl 4xl:rounded-3xl hover:-translate-y-2 border-white/5 hover:border-gv-green/30">
                <div class="flex text-gv-yellow mb-4 4xl:mb-8 text-xs 3xl:text-lg 4xl:text-2xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i></div>
                <blockquote class="text-sm 3xl:text-xl 4xl:text-3xl italic mb-4 4xl:mb-8 text-gray-300">"I was not expecting this place to be one of the coolest, chillest, beautifully decorated, and plant loving shop I have ever been to! Totally coming back! Don't walk, run!"</blockquote>
                <figcaption class="text-xs 3xl:text-sm 4xl:text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gv-green">— Kaylee Skiles</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure class="glass-morphism p-6 3xl:p-12 4xl:p-16 rounded-2xl 4xl:rounded-3xl hover:-translate-y-2 border-white/5 hover:border-gv-green/30">
                <div class="flex text-gv-yellow mb-4 4xl:mb-8 text-xs 3xl:text-lg 4xl:text-2xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i></div>
                <blockquote class="text-sm 3xl:text-xl 4xl:text-3xl italic mb-4 4xl:mb-8 text-gray-300">"The selection at Good Vibes is incredible. And the two who head up the place, Rachel and Alex, are phenomenal. Come in for quality product and quality customer experience."</blockquote>
                <figcaption class="text-xs 3xl:text-sm 4xl:text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gv-green">— Timothy Bowles</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure class="glass-morphism p-6 3xl:p-12 4xl:p-16 rounded-2xl 4xl:rounded-3xl hover:-translate-y-2 border-white/5 hover:border-gv-green/30">
                <div class="flex text-gv-yellow mb-4 4xl:mb-8 text-xs 3xl:text-lg 4xl:text-2xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i></div>
                <blockquote class="text-sm 3xl:text-xl 4xl:text-3xl italic mb-4 4xl:mb-8 text-gray-300">"This place is awesome and unique with great products. The best staff and local artists. I'm always taken care of so good here. I can't wait to go back!!!"</blockquote>
                <figcaption class="text-xs 3xl:text-sm 4xl:text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gv-green">— Lydia Louscher</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
